        <mxCell id="lSMUg6zAjNNxyyKTITEB-4" value="ODD&lt;div&gt;Q1. Design an Instagram like system with following req:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;1: User Login Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;2. Feed service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;3. Follower Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;4. User Engagement Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Restrict non policy compliant posts&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Highlight the use of back fill service&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
